---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Jordi's Blog - Financial Analysis & Market Insights">
  <div class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">
          Financial Analysis & 
          <span class="text-blue-600">Market Insights</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          In-depth research on precious metals markets, investment strategies, and market manipulation analysis. 
          Based on comprehensive data analysis and industry research.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Featured Article -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-700 rounded-xl p-8 text-white mb-16">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">ðŸš¨ BREAKING ANALYSIS</h2>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-4">The Great Silver Squeeze: 338% Gain in 2025</h3>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6 opacity-90">
            Comprehensive analysis reveals how silver has shattered the $60 barrier for the first time in history, 
            driven by structural supply deficits and the collapse of paper market manipulation.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold">$61.69/oz</div>
              <div class="text-sm opacity-80">Current Silver Price</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold">+338%</div>
              <div class="text-sm opacity-80">YTD Performance</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold">820M oz</div>
              <div class="text-sm opacity-80">Supply Deficit</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a 
            href="/posts/the-great-silver-squeeze" 
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-blue-600 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
          >
            Read Full Analysis
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Stats -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Silver-Gold Ratio</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600">68.5:1</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">From 10-year avg of 81.5</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">COMEX Crisis</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-600">37.6M oz</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Vanished in 47 days</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Industrial Demand</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600">680.5M oz</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Record 2024 consumption</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Physical Premiums</h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-600">+15-25%</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Above spot prices</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Recent Posts Section -->
      <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Latest Analysis</h2>
        
        <article class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800">
              Featured Analysis
            </span>
            <time class="text-sm text-gray-500">December 10, 2025</time>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
            <a href="/posts/the-great-silver-squeeze" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
              The Great Silver Squeeze: A Comprehensive Analysis of the Impending Supply Crisis and Market Manipulation
            </a>
          </h3>
          
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Silver has reached an unprecedented inflection point in 2025, with prices shattering the $60 barrier for 
            the first time in history. This comprehensive analysis reveals a perfect storm of structural supply deficits, 
            unprecedented industrial demand, and systemic manipulation approaching its breaking point.
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-xs rounded">Silver</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-xs rounded">Market Analysis</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-xs rounded">Supply Crisis</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 text-xs rounded">Investment</span>
            </div>
            
            <a 
              href="/posts/the-great-silver-squeeze" 
              class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium"
            >
              Read more â†’
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl p-8 text-center mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Stay Updated on Market Developments</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Get insights on precious metals markets, investment opportunities, and analysis of market manipulation. 
          Regular updates on supply/demand dynamics and price forecasts.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a 
            href="/about" 
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-gray-900 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
